<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- mā ạảladẖã ạlạitĩkāla
 ʿalay̱ sayĩdī ạl̊masīḥ̊
 wabiwaʿ̊dihi ạl̊karīmi
 (ạảṭ̊mayỉnũ ạảs̊tarīḥ̊)

[C1]
   ạlqrạr: yā ại̹lahī ại̹nĩy wātẖiq̊
   bal̊ mutãkiluⁿ ʿalaẙk̊
   kulũ waʿ̊diⁿ min̊ka ṣādiq̊
   (hā ạảnā baẙna yadaẙk̊)

[V2]
 2- mā ạảladẖã ạlạitĩkāla
 ʿalay̱ rabĩy dẖī ạl̊bahā
 man̊ waʿad̊nā ạản̊ yakūna
 (maʿ̊nā ḥatãy̱ ạl̊mun̊tahay̱)

[V3]
 3- mā ạảladẖã ạlạitĩkāla
 ʿalay̱ muf̊tadī ạlạảnām̊
 fah̊wa yuʿ̊ṭīnī surūraⁿạ
 (rāḥaẗaⁿ kadẖā salạm̊)</lyrics>
<title>mạ ạ̉ldẖ ạlạtkạl</title>
<hymn_number>8449</hymn_number>
</song>